Code changes must update AGENTS.md/ADR/SSOT. Documentation must stay in sync with code changes.

## Documentation Updates Required

- **AGENTS.md**: Update when code changes affect agent behavior or workflows
- **ADRs**: Create/update when architectural decisions are made (see Rule 029)
- **SSOT docs**: Update when schemas, contracts, or interfaces change
- **README.md**: Update when user-facing features or usage changes

## Enforcement

- **Rule 058**: Docs sync validation is part of mandatory housekeeping workflow
- **rules_guard.py**: Automated validation in CI/pre-commit
- **Manual verification**: Verify docs updated during housekeeping checklist

